original_title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Hering Avenue
text:
East Gunhill Road, south side, east from Hering Ave. The letter boxes are in front of No. 1164, and the 1-story frame real estate office is No. 1170 at the S.W. corner of Tenbroeck Ave.

June 1, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.

Farming in the Bronx: A farmer plowing his field on the east side of Ferris Avenue, between Philip and Randall Avenues.

July 24, 1928

P. L. Sperr

(2) A scene on the north side of E. Gunhill Road, between Boston Road and Givan Avenue.

June 1, 1928

P.L. Sperr

(3) Farming in the Bronx: An orchard on West Farms Road, north of E. 173rd Street.

May 31, 1928

P. L. Sperr
